{% assign faq_uid = 'next-steps-tape-accordion-1' %}

<button
  class="faq-card faq-card--white faq-card--left-align"
  type="button"
  aria-expanded="{% if isOpen %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}"
  aria-controls="faq-content-{{ faq_uid }}"
  id="{{ faq_uid }}"
  data-faq-trigger
>
  <div class="faq-card__indicator"></div>
  <p class="faq-card__question type-p">📮 Send Us Your Tapes!</p>
  <div
    class="faq-card__content"
    id="faq-content-{{ faq_uid }}"
    role="region"
    aria-labelledby="{{ faq_uid }}"
    {% unless isOpen %}
      hidden
    {% endunless %}
    data-faq-content
  >
    <div class="faq-card__inner">
      <div class="faq-answer rich-text">
        <p>
          <strong><u>Mail in:</u></strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Upon order completion, you'll be guided through your next steps. To ship to our digitization facility, include
          your order number with your tapes in a securely packed box or bubble mailer. Use ample padding material to
          ensure your tapes arrive safely and protected from damage.
        </p>

        <p>📬 Mail your tapes to us: <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dynamic location go here</a></p>

        <p>📦 Pack your order with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your video/audio tapes</li>
          <li>Your printed order slip</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card-or-divider type-p"></div>
      <div class="faq-answer rich-text">
        <p>
          <strong><u>Drop-off:</u></strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Upon order completion you'll be guided through your next steps. To drop off, include your order number with
          your tapes in a securely sealed bag or box to protect them during transport.
        </p>

        <p>📍 Drop off your tapes at: Any Bellows drop-off location</p>

        <p>📦 What to bring:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your video/audio tapes</li>
          <li>Your printed order slip</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</button>
